text: Henry Cole LITTLE SIMON New York London Toronto Sydney New Delhi START OF BOOK
the middle of New York City
an ice rink to skate on
the only families at the zoo
Two penguins in the penguin house
no baby chick to feed and cuddle and love
the children who came to playing in the other penguins
all the other penguins in the penguin house
all the families in the big city around them
another penguin couple named Betty and Porkey
